    <p class="lead">Style, simplified. GroomMate is your modern solution for booking grooming appointments online. Say goodbye to waiting on the phone and hello to effortless scheduling.</p>
    <p><a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Account","Views")" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book Now &raquo;</a></p>
